        <introduction>
            <para>
                DigitalRise Graphics provides new content importers and processors, which can be used in an
                XNA content project. This topic explains how to build assets using the new content
                importers and processors.
            </para>
            <autoOutline>1</autoOutline>
        </introduction>


        <section address="Importers">
            <title>Content importers</title>
            <content>
                <para>
                    DigitalRise Graphics provides the following content importers:
                </para>
                <table>
                    <tableHeader>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    Name
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    Type
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    Description
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tableHeader>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                "Material - DigitalRise Graphics"
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false">T:DigitalRise.Graphics.Content.Pipeline.DRMaterialImporter</codeEntityReference>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                Imports materials.
                                See <link xlink:href="9e0c41a1-9e6b-4e78-95a0-831ec4fada0a" />.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                "Model - DigitalRise Graphics"
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false">T:DigitalRise.Graphics.Content.Pipeline.DRModelImporter</codeEntityReference>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                Imports models from model description files.
                                See <link xlink:href="c5deb208-188f-4995-bb6b-c682a3997d40" />.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                "Texture - DigitalRise Graphics"
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false">T:DigitalRise.Graphics.Content.Pipeline.DRTextureImporter</codeEntityReference>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>
                                Imports textures. Extends and replaces the XNA Texture Importer.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </table>
            </content>
        </section>


